; Shared GLCD control-character definitions used by glcd_library.z80
CR:     .equ 0DH                 ; Carriage Return
LF:     .equ 0AH                 ; Line Feed
BS:     .equ 08H                 ; Backspace
BKSP:   .equ 08H                 ; Backspace (alias)
HT:     .equ 09H                 ; Horizontal Tab
TAB:    .equ 09H                 ; Horizontal Tab (alias)
SPACE:  .equ 20H                 ; Space
